<subSubSection pageId="635" pageNumber="636" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="635" pageNumber="636">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="635" pageNumber="636">This species ranges from New Brunswick (Webster and Bousquet 2008: 20) to southern Manitoba (Lindroth 1969a: 964; Roughley et al. 2010: 230), south to central Nebraska (Loup County, Foster F. Purrington pers. comm. 2010), northern Indiana, and New Jersey (Ball 1959: 219).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
