<subSubSection pageId="635" pageNumber="636" type="note">
<paragraph pageId="635" pageNumber="636">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="635" pageNumber="636">
This species has been referred to the subgenus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Stephens" authorityYear="1828" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Trimorphus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="635" pageNumber="636" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="635" pageNumber="636">Trimorphus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Stephens (type species: 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Stephens" authorityYear="1828" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Trimorphus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="635" pageNumber="636" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="scapularis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="635" pageNumber="636">Trimorphus scapularis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Stephens, 1828 (= 
<taxonomicName class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Carabus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="635" pageNumber="636" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sodalis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="635" pageNumber="636">Carabus sodalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Duftschmid, 1812)) by Ball (1959) but Lindroth (1969a: 962) concluded that it is probably more closely related to members of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Ragusa" authorityYear="1884" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Baudia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="635" pageNumber="636" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="635" pageNumber="636">Baudia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
than to those of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Stephens" authorityYear="1828" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Trimorphus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="635" pageNumber="636" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="635" pageNumber="636">Trimorphus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
